computeContaminationProb() - Method in class covidSimulation.InfectedWithoutSymptomsAgent
Returns the more realistic contamination probability by taking into account the fact that this agent has symptoms and wears or not the mask : probInf * FACTOR_WITH_SYMPTOMS if he does not wear the mask, probInf * FACTOR_WITH_SYMPTOMS * FACTOR_WITH_MASK if he wears the mask.
